2.0 Building the Editor 
======================= 
   The user can upload images to be part of the post.
   More than one image means creation of Bigjara carousel.
   For now , my engineering capability is not yet able to break 
   the problem of streaming files.
   Although , i'm seriously working on that.
   The editor can now do quite a lot.
   I simplified the coding using Array , and functions.
   